summary: Providing for the improvement of the alley in Block 7, Plat of Oak Lake Villa Tracts, being the alley between Midvale Avenue North and Stone Avenue North from North Northgate Way to North 107th Street; in accord with Resolution 27240 of the City Council of the City of Seattle; creating Local Improvement District No.----------and providing for payment of the cost and expense of the improvement by special assessments upon property within the district by payment by bonds.
